The cruiseship Adreanna has set sail to Mexico. On board are berthed a group of sex crazed swingers, ready for some fun in the sun. Who's in charge of these hot blooded hedonists? So get ready for the all action blockbuster "Dangerous Tides" shot on location on the Pacific Ocean with an all-star cast. Lots of girls. Lots of seamen
